    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >受经典启发，为现代观众量身打造。</h2>这是一个以中世纪幻想世界为背景的复仇故事……一种带有现代致命火力的疯狂。与不死族、变种人、外星人、机器和野兽的军队作战，以夺回属于你的东西，并为这片土地带来一些表面上的和平。谁知道——如果你足够透彻，你甚至可能会发现这个王国的学者们早已失传的历史。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175090/extras/fc5cb1e52afa3aa0bf55992262072bc4.poster.avif?t=1713369673\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175090/extras/fc5cb1e52afa3aa0bf55992262072bc4.webm?t=1713369673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175090/extras/fc5cb1e52afa3aa0bf55992262072bc4.mp4?t=1713369673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Knights &amp; Guns将您带入一个危险的世界，在那里您将与朋友一起对抗恶魔、食尸鬼和鬼魂。使用散弹枪、激光和骑士精神来克服每一个障碍。成为最好的骑士 - 一个拿着枪的人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175090/extras/e3d00a3d39a23fffffcdc6147429571d.poster.avif?t=1713369673\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175090/extras/e3d00a3d39a23fffffcdc6147429571d.webm?t=1713369673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175090/extras/e3d00a3d39a23fffffcdc6147429571d.mp4?t=1713369673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏内容：<br>• 在各个阶段与出色的BOSS战斗！<br>• 征服非线性世界！冲过150多个手工制作的关卡，或按照自己的节奏享受游戏，寻找秘密和特殊路线！<br>• 整个游戏专为单人游戏或多人合作游戏而设计。随时邀请朋友获得额外的火力和混乱。<br>• 查看所有令人敬畏的盔甲套装，当然还有所有的枪支！激光、散弹枪、榴弹发射器、狙击步枪……全都在这！<br>• 超过30种独特的枪支。<br>• 超过25种敌人，5种小BOSS和3种BOSS。其中大多数也有不同的颜色。<br>• 30套独特的骑士盔甲。额外的保护和额外的风格！<br>• 陷阱、宝箱、钥匙、知识卷轴、怪物书籍…<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175090/extras/c478f9cccc19e7bf4bded76af2137633.poster.avif?t=1713369673\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175090/extras/c478f9cccc19e7bf4bded76af2137633.webm?t=1713369673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175090/extras/c478f9cccc19e7bf4bded76af2137633.mp4?t=1713369673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
